{"tid":452242,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"讚唔讚成用群眾力量令五毛收皮","createTime":"2017-10-30T04:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T17:27:10.000Z","uid":58358,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed95e8d321691c0e70f57fcb5aa7df1fda252ab2","tid":452242,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"五毛畀人 report 過左某個數量<br />\n<br />\nsystem 自動隱藏佢地出既所有post<br />\n<br />\n轉為顯示一行字講返佢因為被太多人投訴以至個 post 被隱藏，但有得選擇顯示內容<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做如何?"},{"pid":"97b54deb91bfa4cb525279dfede87ac022e2041c","tid":452242,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:11:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>絕對贊成，先搞以下公認仆街冚家鏟<br />\n<br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n<br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n<br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n<br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n<br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\n<br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\n<br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\n<br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\n<br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"23692dde7599a11b936388bb77d17d657e9061d3","tid":452242,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"會員之間既問題會員自己解決<br />\n唔洗勞煩 admin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e993a5feb5d253fa4b23a2468693eb899f786c26","tid":452242,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T20:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會員之間既問題會員自己解決<br />\n唔洗勞煩 admin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>又或者每個重要投訴隨機抽十零個會員裁決，好似陪審團制度咁，唔肯參與即暫時BAM到履行義務為止</strong></span>"},{"pid":"81e1b2da0afa47de13d20e0aa8f29b3d241a05ee","tid":452242,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T21:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會員之間既問題會員自己解決<br />\n唔洗勞煩 admin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>又或者每個重要投訴隨機抽十零個會員裁決，好似陪審團制度咁，唔肯參與即暫時BAM到履行義務為止</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n十幾個唔夠 一陣成班五毛溝淡咪仆街"},{"pid":"bdc97f6d0b46141ee28a7db439fefb6482581630","tid":452242,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T22:22:02.000Z","msg":"cc台式民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da066f88fa607466f808e89a0cfbc80c94103eba","tid":452242,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:24:08.000Z","msg":"set 1000-200